dct_title_s:
Die eigentliche und warhafftige geſtalt der Erden und des Meers. Cosmographia
          Vniversalis
dct_description_sm:
"Jerusalem is sited in the centre of the map since it was regarded then as the centre of
        the world." Portion of America appears, Die Newe Welt. The sea contains four sea monsters.
        Top left: 8. Top right: 9.
